Bakers Baked Bread.

When a baker bakes breads, the breads get baked by the baker.

Ingredients.
0 breads
3 croissants
1 berlin boule

Method.
Put breads into the mixing bowl.
Bake croissants.
 Take croissants from refrigerator.
 Add croissants to the mixing bowl.
 Put croissants into the 4th mixing bowl.
 Add berlin boule to the 4th mixing bowl.
 Fold croissants into the 4th mixing bowl.
Watch croissants until baked.
Pour contents of the mixing bowl into the baking dish.

Serves 1.
